msgid "# Prepare inputs for model forwarding"
msgstr "# 准备模型前向传播的输入"

msgid "## Purpose"
msgstr "## 目的"

msgid "Information required to perform model forward pass:"
msgstr "执行模型前向传播所需的信息："

msgid ""
"- the inputs\n"
"- the corresponding attention metadata of the inputs"
msgstr ""
"- 输入数据\n"
"- 输入数据对应的注意力元数据"

msgid ""
"The following diagram shows what we should prepare for model inference."
msgstr "下图展示了模型推理需要准备的内容。"

msgid ""
"Therefore, as long as we have these two pieces of information mentioned "
"above, we can perform the model's forward propagation."
msgstr "因此，只要具备上述两类信息，即可执行模型的前向传播。"

msgid ""
"This document will explain **how we obtain the inputs and their "
"corresponding attention metadata**."
msgstr "本文档将说明**如何获取输入及其对应的注意力元数据**。"

msgid "## Overview"
msgstr "## 概述"

msgid "### 1. Obtain inputs"
msgstr "### 1. 获取输入"

msgid "The workflow of obtaining inputs:"
msgstr "获取输入的工作流程："

msgid ""
"1. Get `token positions`: relative position of each token within its request"
" sequence."
msgstr "1. 获取`token positions`：每个token在其请求序列中的相对位置。"

msgid ""
"2. Get `token indices`: index of each scheduled token in the token table."
msgstr "2. 获取`token indices`：每个被调度token在token表中的索引。"

msgid ""
"3. Get `Token IDs`: using token indices to retrieve the Token IDs from "
"**token id table**."
msgstr "3. 获取`Token IDs`：通过token索引从**token id表**中检索Token ID。"

msgid ""
"At last, these `Token IDs` are required to be fed into a model, and "
"`positions` should also be sent into the model to create `RoPE` (Rotary "
"positional embedding). Both of them are the inputs of the model."
msgstr ""
"最后，这些`Token IDs`需要输入模型，同时`positions`也需要传入模型以生成`RoPE`（旋转位置编码）。这两者都是模型的输入。"

msgid ""
"**Note**: The `Token IDs` are the inputs of a model, so we also call them "
"`Input IDs`."
msgstr "**注意**：`Token IDs`是模型的输入，因此我们也称其为`Input IDs`。"

msgid "### 2. Build inputs attention metadata"
msgstr "### 2. 构建输入注意力元数据"

msgid "A model requires these attention metadata during the forward pass:"
msgstr "模型在前向传播过程中需要以下注意力元数据："

msgid ""
"- `query start location`: start and end location of each request corresponding to the scheduled tokens.\n"
"- `sequence length`: length of each request including both computed tokens and newly scheduled tokens.\n"
"- `number of computed tokens`: number of computed tokens for each request.\n"
"- `number of requests`: number of requests in this batch.\n"
"- `number of tokens`: total number of scheduled tokens in this batch.\n"
"- **`block table`**: translates the logical address (within its sequence) of each block to its global physical address in the device's memory.\n"
"- `max query len`: the longest scheduled tokens length in this request batch.\n"
"- `slot mapping`: indices of each token that input token will be stored into.\n"
"- `attention mask`: mask matrix applied to attention scores before softmax to control which tokens can attend to each other (usually a causal attention)."
msgstr ""
"- `query start location`：每个请求对应被调度token的起始和结束位置。\n"
"- `sequence length`：每个请求的长度，包括已计算token和新调度的token。\n"
"- `number of computed tokens`：每个请求已计算的token数量。\n"
"- `number of requests`：当前批次中的请求数量。\n"
"- `number of tokens`：当前批次中被调度的token总数。\n"
"- **`block table`**：将每个块的逻辑地址（在其序列内）转换为设备内存中的全局物理地址。\n"
"- `max query len`：当前请求批次中最长的被调度token长度。\n"
"- `slot mapping`：每个输入token将被存储到的索引位置。\n"
"- `attention mask`：在softmax之前应用于注意力分数的掩码矩阵，用于控制哪些token可以相互关注（通常为因果注意力）。"

msgid "## Before start"
msgstr "## 开始之前"

msgid "There are mainly three types of variables."
msgstr "主要存在三种类型的变量。"

msgid ""
"- token level: represents one attribute corresponding to each scheduled token, so the length of this variable is the number of scheduled tokens.\n"
"- request level: represents one attribute of each scheduled request, whose length usually is the number of scheduled requests. (`query start location` is a special case, which has one more element.)\n"
"- system level:\n"
"  1. **Token IDs table**: stores the token IDs (i.e. the inputs of a model) of each request. The shape of this table is `(max num request, max model len)`. Here, `max num request` is the maximum count of concurrent requests allowed in a forward batch and `max model len` is the maximum token count that can be handled at one request sequence in this model.\n"
"  2. **Block table**: translates the logical address (within its sequence) of each block to its global physical address in the device's memory. The shape of this table is `(max num request, max model len / block size)`"
msgstr ""
"- token级别：表示每个被调度token对应的一个属性，因此该变量的长度为被调度token的数量。\n"
"- request级别：表示每个被调度请求的一个属性，其长度通常为被调度请求的数量。（`query start location`是一个特例，它多一个元素。）\n"
"- 系统级别：\n"
"  1. **Token IDs表**：存储每个请求的token ID（即模型的输入）。该表的形状为`(max num request, max model len)`。其中，`max num request`是前向批次中允许的最大并发请求数，`max model len`是该模型中单个请求序列能处理的最大token数量。\n"
"  2. **Block表**：将每个块的逻辑地址（在其序列内）转换为设备内存中的全局物理地址。该表的形状为`(max num request, max model len / block size)`"

msgid ""
"**Note**: Both of these two tables come from the `_update_states` method "
"before **preparing inputs**. You can take a look if you need more "
"inspiration."
msgstr "**注意**：这两个表都来自**准备输入**之前的`_update_states`方法。如需更多启发，可以查看该方法。"

msgid "### Tips"
msgstr "### 提示"

msgid ""
"Simply put, a `token ID` is an **integer** (usually `int32`), which represents a token.\n"
"Example of `Token ID`:"
msgstr ""
"简单来说，`token ID`是一个**整数**（通常为`int32`），代表一个token。\n"
"`Token ID`示例："

msgid "## Go through details"
msgstr "## 详细流程"

msgid "Assumptions:"
msgstr "假设条件："

msgid ""
"- maximum number of tokens that can be scheduled at once: 10\n"
"- `block size`: 2\n"
"- Totally schedule 3 requests. Their prompt lengths are 3, 2, and 8 respectively.\n"
"- `max model length`: 12 (the maximum token count that can be handled at one request sequence in a model)."
msgstr ""
"- 单次最大可调度token数：10\n"
"- `block size`：2\n"
"- 总共调度3个请求。它们的提示长度分别为3、2和8。\n"
"- `max model length`：12（模型中单个请求序列能处理的最大token数量）。"

msgid ""
"These assumptions are configured at the beginning when starting vLLM. They "
"are not fixed, so you can manually set them."
msgstr "这些假设条件在启动vLLM时配置。它们并非固定不变，您可以手动设置。"

msgid "### Step 1: All requests in the prefill phase"
msgstr "### 步骤1：所有请求处于预填充阶段"

msgid ""
"As the maximum number of tokens that can be scheduled is 10, the scheduled "
"tokens of each request can be represented as `{'0': 3, '1': 2, '2': 5}`. "
"Note that `request_2` uses chunked prefill, leaving 3 prompt tokens "
"unscheduled."
msgstr ""
"由于单次最大可调度token数为10，每个请求的被调度token可表示为`{'0': 3, '1': 2, '2': "
"5}`。注意，`request_2`使用了分块预填充，剩余3个提示token未被调度。"

msgid "##### 1. Get token positions"
msgstr "##### 1. 获取token位置"

msgid ""
"First, determine which request each token belongs to: tokens 0–2 are "
"assigned to **request_0**, tokens 3–4 to **request_1**, and tokens 5–9 to "
"**request_2**. To represent this mapping, we use `request indices`, for "
"example, `request indices`: `[0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2]`."
msgstr ""
"首先，确定每个token所属的请求：token 0–2分配给**request_0**，token 3–4分配给**request_1**，token "
"5–9分配给**request_2**。为了表示这种映射关系，我们使用`request indices`，例如`request "
"indices`：`[0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2]`。"

msgid ""
"For each request, use **the number of computed tokens** + **the relative "
"position of current scheduled tokens** (`request_0: [0 + 0, 0 + 1, 0 + 2]`, "
"`request_1: [0 + 0, 0 + 1]`, `request_2: [0 + 0, 0 + 1,..., 0 + 4]`) and "
"then concatenate them together (`[0, 1, 2, 0, 1, 0, 1, 2, 3, 4]`)."
msgstr ""
"对于每个请求，使用**已计算token数** + **当前被调度token的相对位置**（`request_0: [0 + 0, 0 + 1, 0 + "
"2]`，`request_1: [0 + 0, 0 + 1]`，`request_2: [0 + 0, 0 + 1,..., 0 + "
"4]`），然后将它们拼接在一起（`[0, 1, 2, 0, 1, 0, 1, 2, 3, 4]`）。"

msgid ""
"Note: there is a more efficient way (using `request indices`) to create "
"positions in actual code."
msgstr "注意：在实际代码中，有一种更高效的方法（使用`request indices`）来创建位置。"

msgid ""
"Finally, `token positions` can be obtained as `[0, 1, 2, 0, 1, 0, 1, 2, 3, "
"4]`. This variable is **token level**."
msgstr ""
"最终，`token positions`为`[0, 1, 2, 0, 1, 0, 1, 2, 3, 4]`。该变量属于**token级别**。"

msgid "##### 2. Get token indices"
msgstr "##### 2. 获取token索引"

msgid ""
"The shape of the current **Token IDs table** is `(max num request, max model"
" len)`."
msgstr "当前**Token IDs表**的形状为`(max num request, max model len)`。"

msgid ""
"Why are these `T_3_5`, `T_3_6`, `T_3_7` in this table without being "
"scheduled?"
msgstr "为什么表中存在`T_3_5`、`T_3_6`、`T_3_7`这些未被调度的token？"

msgid ""
"- We fill all Token IDs in one request sequence to this table at once, but "
"we only retrieve the tokens we scheduled this time. Then we retrieve the "
"remaining Token IDs next time."
msgstr "- 我们将一个请求序列中的所有Token ID一次性填入该表，但只检索本次调度的token。剩余的Token ID将在下次检索。"

msgid "Note that `T_x_x` is an `int32`."
msgstr "注意，`T_x_x` 是一个 `int32` 类型。"

msgid ""
"Let's say `M = max model len`. Then we can use `token positions` together "
"with `request indices` of each token to construct `token indices`."
msgstr ""
"假设 `M = max model len`。然后我们可以使用 `token positions` 以及每个 token 的 `request "
"indices` 来构建 `token indices`。"

msgid ""
"So `token indices` = `[0 + 0 * M, 1 + 0 * M, 2 + 0 * M, 0 + 1 * M, 1 + 1 * "
"M, 0 + 2 * M, 1 + 2 * M, 2 + 2 * M, 3 + 2 * M, 4 + 2 * M]` = `[0, 1, 2, 12, "
"13, 24, 25, 26, 27, 28]`"
msgstr ""
"因此 `token indices` = `[0 + 0 * M, 1 + 0 * M, 2 + 0 * M, 0 + 1 * M, 1 + 1 * "
"M, 0 + 2 * M, 1 + 2 * M, 2 + 2 * M, 3 + 2 * M, 4 + 2 * M]` = `[0, 1, 2, 12, "
"13, 24, 25, 26, 27, 28]`"

msgid "##### 3. Retrieve the Token IDs"
msgstr "##### 3. 获取 Token ID"

msgid ""
"We use `token indices` to select out the corresponding `Input IDs` from the "
"token table. The pseudocode is as follows:"
msgstr "我们使用 `token indices` 从 token 表中选出对应的 `Input IDs`。伪代码如下："

msgid "As mentioned before, we refer to these `Token IDs` as `Input IDs`."
msgstr "如前所述，我们将这些 `Token IDs` 称为 `Input IDs`。"

msgid ""
"- `Input IDs` = `[T_0_0, T_0_1, T_0_2, T_1_0, T_1_1, T_2_0, T_2_1, T_3_2, "
"T_3_3, T_3_4]`"
msgstr ""
"- `Input IDs` = `[T_0_0, T_0_1, T_0_2, T_1_0, T_1_1, T_2_0, T_2_1, T_3_2, "
"T_3_3, T_3_4]`"

msgid ""
"In the current **Block Table**, we use the first block (i.e. block_0) to "
"mark the unused block. The shape of the block is `(max num request, max "
"model len / block size)`, where `max model len / block size = 12 / 2 = 6`."
msgstr ""
"在当前 **Block Table** 中，我们使用第一个 block（即 block_0）来标记未使用的 block。该 block 的形状为 "
"`(max num request, max model len / block size)`，其中 `max model len / block "
"size = 12 / 2 = 6`。"

msgid "The KV cache block in the device memory is like:"
msgstr "设备内存中的 KV 缓存 block 如下所示："

msgid ""
"Let's say `K = max model len / block size = 6`, and we can get token `device"
" block number`."
msgstr ""
"假设 `K = max model len / block size = 6`，我们可以得到 token 的 `device block "
"number`。"

msgid "The workflow of achieving slot mapping:"
msgstr "实现 slot mapping 的工作流程："

msgid ""
"1. Get `block table indices` using `K`, `positions` and `request indices`."
msgstr "1. 使用 `K`、`positions` 和 `request indices` 获取 `block table indices`。"

msgid ""
"Purpose: For each token, it could be used to select `device block number` "
"from `block table`."
msgstr "目的：对于每个 token，它可用于从 `block table` 中选择 `device block number`。"

msgid "2. Get `device block number` using `block table indices`."
msgstr "2. 使用 `block table indices` 获取 `device block number`。"

msgid ""
"Purpose: `device block number` indicates which device block each token "
"belongs to."
msgstr "目的：`device block number` 指示每个 token 属于哪个设备 block。"

msgid "3. Get `block offsets` using `positions` and `block size`."
msgstr "3. 使用 `positions` 和 `block size` 获取 `block offsets`。"

msgid ""
"Purpose: `block offsets` indicates the offsets of each token within a block."
msgstr "目的：`block offsets` 指示每个 token 在 block 内的偏移量。"

msgid ""
"4. construct `slot mapping` using `device block number` and `block offsets`."
msgstr "4. 使用 `device block number` 和 `block offsets` 构建 `slot mapping`。"

msgid ""
"Purpose: we can use `slot mapping` to store Token IDs into token slots."
msgstr "目的：我们可以使用 `slot mapping` 将 Token ID 存储到 token 槽位中。"

msgid "Details:"
msgstr "详细信息："

msgid ""
"1. (**Token level**) Use a simple formula to calculate `block table indices`: `request indices * K + positions / block size`. So it equals `[0 * 6 + 0 / 2, 0 * 6 + 1 / 2, 0 * 6 + 2 / 2, 1 * 6 + 0 / 2, 1 * 6 + 1 / 2, 2 * 6 + 0 / 2, 2 * 6 + 1 / 2, 2 * 6 + 2 / 2, 2 * 6 + 3 / 2, 2 * 6 + 4 / 2] = [0, 0, 1, 6, 6, 12, 12, 13, 13, 14]`. This could be used to select `device block number` from `block table`.\n"
"2. (**Token level**) Use `block table indices` to select out `device block number` for each scheduled token. The pseudocode is `block_numbers = block_table[block_table_indices]`. So `device block number=[1, 1, 2, 3, 3, 4, 4, 5, 5, 6]`\n"
"3. (**Token level**) `block offsets` could be computed by `block offsets = positions % block size = [0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 1, 0]`.\n"
"4. Finally, use `block offsets` and `device block number` to create `slot mapping`: `device block number * block size + block_offsets = [2, 3, 4, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10, 11, 12]`"
msgstr ""
"1. (**Token 级别**) 使用简单公式计算 `block table indices`：`request indices * K + positions / block size`。因此结果为 `[0 * 6 + 0 / 2, 0 * 6 + 1 / 2, 0 * 6 + 2 / 2, 1 * 6 + 0 / 2, 1 * 6 + 1 / 2, 2 * 6 + 0 / 2, 2 * 6 + 1 / 2, 2 * 6 + 2 / 2, 2 * 6 + 3 / 2, 2 * 6 + 4 / 2] = [0, 0, 1, 6, 6, 12, 12, 13, 13, 14]`。这可用于从 `block table` 中选择 `device block number`。\n"
"2. (**Token 级别**) 使用 `block table indices` 为每个调度的 token 选出 `device block number`。伪代码为 `block_numbers = block_table[block_table_indices]`。因此 `device block number=[1, 1, 2, 3, 3, 4, 4, 5, 5, 6]`\n"
"3. (**Token 级别**) `block offsets` 可通过 `block offsets = positions % block size = [0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 1, 0]` 计算。\n"
"4. 最后，使用 `block offsets` 和 `device block number` 创建 `slot mapping`：`device block number * block size + block_offsets = [2, 3, 4, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10, 11, 12]`"

msgid ""
"(**Request level**) As we know the scheduled token count is `[3, 2, 5]`:"
msgstr "(**Request 级别**) 由于我们知道调度的 token 数量为 `[3, 2, 5]`："

msgid ""
"- (**Request level**) Use prefix sum to calculate `query start location`: `[0, 3, 5, 10]`.\n"
"- (**Request level**) All tokens in step 1 are in the prefill stage, and the computed tokens count is 0; then `sequence length` = `[3, 2, 5]`.\n"
"- (**Request level**) As mentioned above, `number of computed tokens` are all 0s: `[0, 0, 0]`.\n"
"- `number of requests`: `3`\n"
"- (**Request level**) `number of tokens`: `[3, 2, 5]`\n"
"- `max query len`: `5`\n"
"- (**Token level**) `slot mapping`: `[2, 3, 4, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10, 11, 12]`\n"
"- `attention mask`: For all requests that initiate a prefill process, we simply create only one mask matrix for reuse across different requests. The shape of this mask matrix is `5 * 5`:"
msgstr ""
"- (**Request 级别**) 使用前缀和计算 `query start location`：`[0, 3, 5, 10]`。\n"
"- (**Request 级别**) 步骤 1 中的所有 token 都处于 prefill 阶段，且已计算的 token 数量为 0；因此 `sequence length` = `[3, 2, 5]`。\n"
"- (**Request 级别**) 如上所述，`number of computed tokens` 全为 0：`[0, 0, 0]`。\n"
"- `number of requests`：`3`\n"
"- (**Request 级别**) `number of tokens`：`[3, 2, 5]`\n"
"- `max query len`：`5`\n"
"- (**Token 级别**) `slot mapping`：`[2, 3, 4, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10, 11, 12]`\n"
"- `attention mask`：对于所有发起 prefill 过程的请求，我们仅创建一个掩码矩阵以便在不同请求间复用。该掩码矩阵的形状为 `5 * 5`："

msgid "### Step 2: Chunked prefill"
msgstr "### 步骤 2：分块预填充"

msgid ""
"In Step 2, we no longer provide explanations or perform calculations; "
"instead, we directly present the final result."
msgstr "在步骤 2 中，我们不再提供解释或进行计算，而是直接给出最终结果。"

msgid "#### Obtain inputs"
msgstr "#### 获取输入"

msgid "Scheduled token of each request: `{'0': 1, '1': 1, '2': 3}`"
msgstr "每个请求调度的 token：`{'0': 1, '1': 1, '2': 3}`"

msgid ""
"1. `request indices`: `[0, 1, 2, 2, 2]`\n"
"2. `token positions`: `[3, 2, 5, 6, 7]`"
msgstr ""
"1. `request indices`：`[0, 1, 2, 2, 2]`\n"
"2. `token positions`：`[3, 2, 5, 6, 7]`"

msgid "Current **Token IDs table**:"
msgstr "当前 **Token ID 表**："

msgid ""
"**Note**: **T_0_3**, **T_1_2** are new Token IDs of **request_0** and "
"**request_1** respectively. They are sampled from the output of the model."
msgstr ""
"**注意**：**T_0_3**、**T_1_2** 分别是 **request_0** 和 **request_1** 的新 Token "
"ID。它们是从模型输出中采样得到的。"

msgid ""
"3. `token indices`: `[3, 14, 29, 30, 31]`\n"
"4. `Input IDs`: `[T_0_3, T_1_2, T_3_5, T_3_6, T_3_7]`"
msgstr ""
"3. `token indices`：`[3, 14, 29, 30, 31]`\n"
"4. `Input IDs`：`[T_0_3, T_1_2, T_3_5, T_3_6, T_3_7]`"

msgid "#### Build inputs attention metadata"
msgstr "#### 构建输入注意力元数据"

msgid ""
"We allocate the blocks `7` and `8` to `request_1` and `request_2` "
"respectively, as they need more space in device to store KV cache following "
"token generation or chunked prefill."
msgstr ""
"我们将 block `7` 和 `8` 分别分配给 `request_1` 和 `request_2`，因为它们在 token "
"生成或分块预填充后需要在设备上占用更多空间来存储 KV 缓存。"

msgid "Current **Block Table**:"
msgstr "当前 **Block Table**："

msgid "KV cache block in the device memory:"
msgstr "设备内存中的 KV 缓存 block："

msgid ""
"1. (**Token level**) `block table indices`: `[1, 7, 14, 15, 15]`\n"
"2. (**Token level**) `device block number`: `[2, 7, 6, 8, 8]`\n"
"3. (**Token level**) `block offsets`: `[1, 0, 1, 0, 1]`\n"
"4. (**Token level**) `slot mapping`: `[5, 14, 13, 16, 17]`"
msgstr ""
"1. (**Token 级别**) `block table indices`：`[1, 7, 14, 15, 15]`\n"
"2. (**Token 级别**) `device block number`：`[2, 7, 6, 8, 8]`\n"
"3. (**Token 级别**) `block offsets`：`[1, 0, 1, 0, 1]`\n"
"4. (**Token 级别**) `slot mapping`：`[5, 14, 13, 16, 17]`"

msgid "Scheduled token count: `[1, 1, 3]`"
msgstr "调度的 token 数量：`[1, 1, 3]`"

msgid "- `query start location`: `[0, 1, 2, 5]`"
msgstr "- `query start location`：`[0, 1, 2, 5]`"

msgid "- `sequence length`: `[4, 3, 8]`"
msgstr "- `sequence length`：`[4, 3, 8]`"

msgid "- `number of computed tokens`: `[3, 2, 5]`"
msgstr "- `number of computed tokens`：`[3, 2, 5]`"

msgid "- `number of requests`: `3`"
msgstr "- `number of requests`：`3`"

